PrecisAmendments to the CANADIAN INTERNATIONAL TRADE TRIBUNAL REGULATIONS which consolidate the existing definitions of "other interested parties" and extend their application to notification procedures for safeguard extension inquiries and mid-term reviews, and specify the kinds of information or reviews the Tribunal shall take into account.
